sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Platform Ingress
    participant Server as NeMo Guardrails Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant InputRails as Input Rails<br/>(Content Safety, Jailbreak, SDD)
    participant ContentSafety as Content Safety Model<br/>HTTP(S)
    participant Jailbreak as Jailbreak Detection<br/>HTTP(S)
    participant LLM as LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OutputRails as Output Rails<br/>(Content Safety, Hallucination, Self-Check)
    participant Redis as Redis (Optional)<br/>6379/TCP

    Note over Client,Redis: Flow 1: Chat Completion with Guardrails

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP (Platform TLS)<br/>Authorization header forwarded
    Server->>Server: Select engine<br/>(IORails or LLMRails)

    opt Thread persistence enabled
        Server->>Redis: Load conversation state<br/>TCP/6379 (Optional TLS)
        Redis-->>Server: Thread history
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Server,Jailbreak: Input Rails Phase
        Server->>InputRails: Execute input rails
        InputRails->>ContentSafety: Content safety check<br/>HTTP(S), API key
        ContentSafety-->>InputRails: Classification result (cached)
        InputRails->>Jailbreak: Jailbreak detection<br/>HTTP(S), API key
        Jailbreak-->>InputRails: Detection result (cached)
        InputRails->>InputRails: Sensitive data detection<br/>(Presidio/spacy, in-process)
        InputRails-->>Server: Rails result (pass/block)
    end

    alt Input blocked
        Server-->>Client: Blocked response<br/>(policy violation message)
    else Input passed
        rect rgb(224, 247, 224)
            Note over Server,LLM: Generation Phase
            Server->>Server: Check LFU cache
            alt Cache hit
                Server->>Server: Return cached response
            else Cache miss
                Server->>LLM: Chat completion request<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token/API key<br/>Authorization header forwarded
                LLM-->>Server: LLM response
                Server->>Server: Cache response (LFU)
            end
        end

        rect rgb(224, 232, 255)
            Note over Server,ContentSafety: Output Rails Phase
            Server->>OutputRails: Execute output rails
            OutputRails->>ContentSafety: Content safety check<br/>HTTP(S), API key
            ContentSafety-->>OutputRails: Classification result
            OutputRails->>OutputRails: Hallucination self-check<br/>(via LLM)
            OutputRails->>OutputRails: Output self-check<br/>(via LLM)
            OutputRails-->>Server: Rails result (pass/block)
        end

        opt Thread persistence enabled
            Server->>Redis: Save conversation state<br/>TCP/6379
        end

        Server-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(OpenAI-compatible format)
    end

    Note over Client,Redis: Flow 2: Guardrail Checks (RHOAI-Specific)

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP (Platform TLS)
    Server->>Server: Evaluate rails per-message<br/>(no LLM generation)
    Server->>ContentSafety: Rail evaluation<br/>HTTP(S)
    ContentSafety-->>Server: Rail results
    Server-->>Client: Per-message rail results<br/>(pass/fail per rail)

    Note over Client,Redis: Flow 3: Knowledge Base Embedding Search

    Client->>Server: Query with KB-enabled config
    Server->>Server: Generate embedding<br/>(FastEmbed, in-process)
    Server->>Server: Vector similarity search<br/>(Annoy index, in-process)
    Server->>LLM: RAG query with retrieved chunks<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    LLM-->>Server: Grounded response
    Server-->>Client: Response with KB context
